If you cannot find boost/heap library, please download
boost.1.50.0 (or later) from
http://sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/boost/1.50.0/boost_1_50_0.tar.gz/download

If you are an administrator:
Download it and put it in /usr/local/include/boost_1_50_0
Create a soft link
(ln -s /usr/local/include/boost_1_50_0/boost /usr/local/include/)
Then make again.

If you are not a ministrator:
Download the file and put it in some directory
Modify the Makefile so -I redirect to /SOMEWHERE/boost_1_50_0/boost/
Then make again.
